{
  "text": "Lu et al. [CITATION_1] provide solutions for designing a business model for sustainable agricultural products utilizing Internet-of-Things (IoT). Aided by IoT, the new business model provides products through networks and e-commerce via electronic data interchange and e-mail online sales contract along with the traditional marketing channels. The convenience of online shopping and instant messaging interoperability are mentioned as new value propositions that IoT can offer for the sustainable agriculture. Lu et al. [CITATION_2] also claim that IoT designs a sophisticated information system in the organizations which arms the businesses to design a customer-centric structure collecting the data and customers' feedbacks and also provides adequate information to the customers.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "7170709",
    "[CITATION_2]": "7170709"
  },
  "bib_entries": {
    "7170709": {
      "title": "Research on the innovation of strategic business model in green agricultural products based on Internet of things (IOT)",
      "abstract": "In China, more and more daily food consuming has transferred from quantity to quality, and with economic development and people's living standards improve, more people like green food. The paper analyzes the characteristics of Green Agricultural products, combining the use of modern information technology-Internet of Things(IOT),and proposed an innovative Business Strategy Model. With the change and innovation of business model, the development of technology and its application are incalculable and sometimes even decisive factor."
    }
  }
}